item.title: CVE-2024-33959|2024-08-06T13:28:46.113Z -- janobe -- janobe%20paypal
item.description: SQL injection vulnerability in PayPal, Credit Card and Debit Card Payment affecting version 1.0. An attacker could exploit this vulnerability by sending a specially crafted query to the server and retrieve all the information stored in it through the following 'categ' in '/admin/mod_reports/printreport.php' parameter.
